# general

- extrastuff.tar.xz contains (config) files that are not taken from any rpm package

# ssh connectivity

- /etc/ssh/sshd_config.d/10_root_login.conf allows root login

# autologin and gfx startup

- /etc/systemd/system/x11-autologin.service uses startx to start an x11 session
- startx runs icewm via /root/.xinitrc
- icewm autostarts firefox via /root/.icewm/startup
- icewm uses our usual installation config from /etc/icewm/preferences.yast2
